    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This car is in pristine, collector-grade condition with a laser-straight body and a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating. There are no rock chips, door dings, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather seats are firm without a single crease, and the interior still carries that fresh, factory scent. Every electronic component, button, and sensor functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to scheduled maintenance\u2014all documented in a comprehensive service history. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot: tight, silent, and powerful. Included are both sets of keys, all original owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
