    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard used-car market. Maintained to a concours-level standard, the exterior remains unblemished, while the interior preserves its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical system has been subjected to a rigorous verification process, ensuring performance that is indistinguishable from its factory-original state. This is an acquisition for the individual who demands perfection and seeks a vehicle of unparalleled preservation.",
