    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and there isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and fall in love! \u2728",
