      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering its signature high-revving power through six individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated dual-VANOS system. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission providing short, precise throws and the variable M differential lock ensuring optimal traction. The chassis is structurally pristine, with the subframe inspected for integrity and the suspension geometry remaining true to factory specifications. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in peak condition, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and preventative maintenance. This is a zero-compromise specimen for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and aesthetic preservation.",
